OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1773331879
OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FAn elderly couple have pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto carrying out a racist assault after
OL,8,Fa video of them abusing a Filipino
OL,9,Fnurse in a park went viral on social
OL,10,Fmedia.
OL,12,FFyona and Michael Bairstow appeared at
OL,13,FBradford Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FWednesday following the incident in
OL,15,FManor Heath Park, Halifax, last August.
OL,17,FA video posted online showed them
OL,18,Fmaking racist comments towards Apple
OL,19,FMoorhouse, a Huddersfield resident who
OL,20,Fhad worked for the NHS for more than a
OL,21,Fdecade.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
