OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FMichael Bairstow, 77, could be seen
OL,7,Fthrowing water at her and saying "go
OL,8,Fback on the boat" while making a
OL,9,Frowing motion.
OL,11,FThe video showed him saying: "Have you
OL,12,Fgot a rubber boat? Did you come across
OL,13,Fthe Channel?"
OL,15,F"Ban the immigrants", he added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
