OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1773331879
OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FFyona Bairstow, 72, confronted Ms
OL,7,FMoorhouse as she filmed the incident,
OL,8,Fgrabbing her arm and her phone and
OL,9,Ftelling her: "I'll make you so bloody
OL,10,Fsick you'll wonder what the hell is
OL,11,Fgoing on."
OL,13,FThe court heard the incident happened
OL,14,Fafter Ms Moorhouse asked the couple to
OL,15,Fcontrol their dog, which had
OL,16,Ffrightened her six-year-old daughter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
