OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FIn a statement, Ms Moorhouse said:
OL,7,F"The reaction was very hostile.
OL,8,F(Michael Bairstow was) telling me to
OL,9,F'go back to your dinghy' and making
OL,10,Fswimming gestures with his arms
OL,11,Ftowards me.
OL,13,F"I said I was a healthcare worker. The
OL,14,Ffemale was calling me a stupid b****."
OL,16,FShe added: "When I tried to walk away
OL,17,Fthe female pulled me back by my
OL,18,Fponytail causing my head to go
OL,19,Fbackwards.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@ApmpD@VpnuD@AOUvD@fO]xD@LOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
