OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1773331879
OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,F"They were very racist towards me,
OL,7,Fthey seemed to want to make everything
OL,8,Fa conversation about immigrants and
OL,9,Fcalling me a slave."
OL,11,FThe court heard that when another
OL,12,Fwoman intervened and told Michael
OL,13,FBairstow to get away from Ms
OL,14,FMoorhouse, he punched her to the left
OL,15,Fside of her face and said: "Sticking
OL,16,Fup for immigrants, who do you think
OL,17,Fyou are?"
OL,19,FHe pleaded to an additional offence of
OL,20,Fassault by beating.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]wD@\OUyD@IO]
