OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FThe couple, of Shelf, Halifax, were
OL,7,Freleased on bail to be sentenced on 15
OL,8,FApril.
OL,10,F'Caring was my passion... but I didn't
OL,11,Fgo back'
OL,13,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,14,Fhearing, Ms Moorhouse, who is a
OL,15,FBritish citizen, said she feels less
OL,16,Fsafe after the incident and "keeps
OL,17,Flooking over my shoulder".
OL,19,F"I feel anxious obviously, every time
OL,20,Fthat I think back, I feel upset," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@]OUyD@YO]{D@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
