OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1773331879
OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,F"It's a big thing, racism, and it
OL,7,Fneeds to be dealt with.
OL,9,F"I've been here since 2009 and never
OL,10,Fhad anything like this before, for 10
OL,11,Fyears, it was fine but now it's got
OL,12,Fworse.
OL,14,F"I used to work in healthcare and I
OL,15,Fwanted to go back but I felt scared
OL,16,F... this happened and I just didn't go
OL,17,Fback.
OL,19,F"Caring was my passion but then this
OL,20,Fhappened and it was hard to go back."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
