OL,3,CCouple admit racist assault after park
OL,4,Cabuse video goes viral
OL,6,FMs Moorhouse added: "At their age they
OL,7,Fshould know better, but obviously they
OL,8,Fdidn't."
OL,10,FThe incident was later condemned by
OL,11,Fthe Nursing and Midwifery Council as
OL,12,F"shocking and disgraceful".
OL,14,FChief executive Paul Rees said:
OL,15,F"Black, Asian and minority ethnic
OL,16,Fpeople ` including nursing and
OL,17,Fmidwifery professionals ` make a huge
OL,18,Fcontribution to our society, in
OL,19,Fgeneral, and to our health services,
OL,20,Fin particular.
OL,26,@nD@UOUpD@HO]wD@AOU
