OL,6,F"Across the health sector, we must
OL,7,Fconfront racism and discrimination
OL,8,Fwherever it occurs, so that every
OL,9,Fnurse, midwife and nursing associate
OL,10,Fcan feel safe, valued and respected as
OL,11,Fthey continue to care for us all."
